{"data":[{"date":"14:13 22/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP HAGL 2-1 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (H1): Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ket-qua-hagl-vs-sai-gon-tran-dau-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-sai-gon-vong-15-vleague-2018-372-189256.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL\u00a0vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3765","checkdouble":"189256"},{"date":"14:18 22/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Thanh H\u00f3a 2-0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (H2): C\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t an to\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/thanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/thanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-vong-15-vleague-2018-372-189257.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP THANH H\u00d3A VS B\u00ccNH D\u01af\u01a0NG</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3764","checkdouble":"189257"},{"date":"17:52 22/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/ket-qua-hagl-vs-sai-gon-tran-dau-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 2-1<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (3'); C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (10'); Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (41')<hr>\r\n<br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1o si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m HAGL khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh Vuong ghi ban tran Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap HAGL t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt ph\u00fat, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap HAGL d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 41, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m65 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3763","checkdouble":"189270"},{"date":"15:09 22/06","title":"Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sau Kroos, Modric v\u00e0 Casemiro.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Thiago-Alcantara-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay Modric \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, Los Blancos \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernaber mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi thay v\u00ec trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Mateo Kovacic.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Kovacic c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda AC Milan v\u00e0 Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, MU v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Kovacic \u1edf l\u1ea1i song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i,&nbsp;Los&nbsp;Blancos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f2n l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Thiago thay Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid nh\u1eafm Thiago Alcantara thay Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Thiago ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayern Munich. HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLopetegui v\u00e0 Thiago c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern Munich nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3762","checkdouble":"189259"},{"date":"15:20 22/06","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup, Lukaku l\u1ecdt t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/toa-sang-o-world-cup-lukaku-lot-tam-ngam-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Real Madrid nh\u1eafm Lukaku thay Benzema</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lukaku kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh gia nh\u1eadp Man United t\u1eeb Everton v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u01b0a k\u00e8m ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Lukaku ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, anh ghi 27 b\u00e0n, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 34 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, t\u00ednh trung b\u00ecnh x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 0,5 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid nh\u1eafm Lukaku thay Benzema h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid nh\u1eafm Lukaku thay Benzema h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/toa-sang-o-world-cup-lukaku-lot-tam-ngam-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;Lukaku c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&nbsp;</em><em>Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1edf M.U nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay, Lukaku \u0111ang ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n h\u1ebft tinh hoa c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n, b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Lukaku th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, BL\u0110 Real d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;ch\u1ea5m&rsquo; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng Karim Benzema, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qua th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfng TBN Diario Gol, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_top\">Real Madrid</span> c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi Karim Benzema v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thay th\u1ebf anh. Benzema \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 9 m\u00f9a \u1edf Bernabeu v\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh ra s\u00e2n 32 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Liga nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Lukaku khi&nbsp;cho r\u1eb1ng anh c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e1 World Cup cho tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-don-thoi-co-mau-thuan-voi-lukaku-hazard-noi-gi-421-189162.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-soi-dong-cung-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-don-thoi-co-mau-thuan-voi-lukaku-hazard-noi-gi-421-189162.html\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Lukaku, Hazard n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nEden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Romelu Lukaku, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu-421-188880.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu-421-188880.html\">Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n kh\u1ee7ng, fan M.U l\u1ea1i l\u00f4i&hellip; Morata ra d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Panama m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u1ee7ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/romelu-lukaku-phat-bieu-day-tinh-nhan-van-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-panama-421-188873.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/romelu-lukaku-phat-bieu-day-tinh-nhan-van-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-panama.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/romelu-lukaku-phat-bieu-day-tinh-nhan-van-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-panama-421-188873.html\">Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00ednh nh\u00e2n v\u0103n sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama</span><br>\r\nRomelu Lukaku n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Panama, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi anh l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3761","checkdouble":"189261"},{"date":"16:09 22/06","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/8/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Paul Pogba l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thay Iniesta</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay CLB Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a I8 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi BHL Barca c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n HLV Ernesto Valverde trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-225-juve-tinh-gay-soc-voi-pogba.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon th\u00ec&nbsp; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Paul Pogba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 HLV Valverde tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Nou Camp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n khi m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Man Utd trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eb1m &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i kh\u00f3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n r\u1ebb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba t\u1eeb Juventus v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Barca, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pogba, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo s\u00e1t Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Christian Eriksen. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n 2 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana n\u1ebfu v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca</span><br>\r\nTottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Spurs c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span><br>\r\nJuventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3760","checkdouble":"189268"},{"date":"15:28 22/06","title":"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Spurs c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Danny Rose kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Ben Davies. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Spurs \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham h\u1ecfi mua Jordi Alba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-tu-choi-theo-duoi-danny-rose-vi-172-188402.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Rose ra \u0111i Spurs s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Theo AS, Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Alba v\u1eabn l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Alba n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alba v\u1edbi Barca v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn Alba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Marcos Alonso\" title=\"hau ve Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/marcos-alonso-co-the-cap-ben-real-madrid-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Alba n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Marcos Alonso</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDon Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca nh\u1eafm Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea thay th\u1ebf Alba, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Alonso nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd nh\u1ea3 Alba cho Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3759","checkdouble":"189262"},{"date":"15:46 22/06","title":"Chelsea gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng \"h\u00e0ng hot\" Seria A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/4/8/trung-ve-phil-jones-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap CLB AS Roma v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, trung v\u1ec7 Kostas Manolas \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, Chelsea.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng Kostas Manolas</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 theo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p Kostas Manolas v\u1edbi CLB AS Roma.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/11/Chelsea-muon-co-Kostas-Manolas-tu-AS-Roma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 26, Kostas Manolas \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 - m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico v\u00e0 gi\u00fap CLB n\u00e0y l\u1eadp&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u khi l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18. Manolas c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a Manolas v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 trong kho\u1ea3ng 36-38 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Manolas.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Manolas, Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eafp ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. S\u1edf d\u0129 The Blues \u01b0a d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Serie A b\u1edfi HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea v\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Maurizio Sarri c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, BL\u0110 Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng &ldquo;gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n&rdquo; h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas-172-189078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas-172-189078.html\">Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Fabregas</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Cesc Fabregas, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3758","checkdouble":"189265"},{"date":"10:21 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thanh-Hoa-vs-Binh-Duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng sau nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i SLNA, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed tinh th\u1ea7n. \u1ede ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Thanh ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2&nbsp;HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea1i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o sau nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m n\u01a1i h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch 4 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1&nbsp; \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 1-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, bao g\u1ed3m tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (3-3). Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, so v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao h\u01a1n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1eeba qua, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Thanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 17 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 5, thua 6.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 3, thua 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc; \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, Minh T\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Hi\u1ebfu, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ofere.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng; Thanh Th\u1ea3o, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ng\u1ecdc M\u1ea1nh, Hu\u1ef3nh Ph\u00fa, Tr\u1ecdng Huy, V\u0103n V\u0169, D\u0169 \u0110\u1ea1t, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Romario.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3757","checkdouble":"189244"},{"date":"10:51 22/06","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rudiger t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u0169ng g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do John Terry \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong khi \u0111\u00f3 David Luiz mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p\u00a0h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Juventus.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chi-354-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-juventus-172-175920.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani</span>, song Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Daniele Rugani. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-2112-Arsenal-chi-dam-tranh-hang-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c Sarri ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay Conte, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 lu\u00f4n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3756","checkdouble":"189240"},{"date":"10:56 22/06","title":"Hazard c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/11/mo-ve-qua-bong-vang-hazard-nen-roi-bo-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 ng\u00f4i sao Eden Hazard n\u00ean chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t CLB danh gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Barcelona.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u00f3ng h\u1ed5i khi kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd theo ch\u00e2n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Antonio Conte chia tay s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/mo-ve-qua-bong-vang-hazard-nen-roi-bo-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp nh\u1eefng Real Madrid hay Barcelona, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo, Lionel Messi hay Gareth Bale m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng, danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh h\u1eb1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Thomas Meunier c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u00f2ng hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Paris Saint-Germain: \u201cN\u1ebfu Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp nh\u1eefng CLB danh gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Barcelona, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn khi sinh c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League c\u0169ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Harry Kane hay Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o ch\u01b0a chia tay n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Hazard \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 chinh chi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Tunisia. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Anh cho ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi-421-188884.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi-421-188884.html\">Hazard: Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1eadm m\u1edbi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, ngay t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3755","checkdouble":"189242"},{"date":"07:44 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-226-khong-con-duong-lui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: G\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e0ng \u0111i v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf kh\u00e2u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf t\u1ed1p cu\u1ed1i TP.HCM, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua g\u1ed3m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/HAGL-Saigon.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u1ea7n&nbsp; gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong n\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL \u00edt khi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi. B\u1edfi khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, NHM c\u0169ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi HAGL, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-2 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00fac n\u00e0y tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mang tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sai Gon vs HAGL\" title=\"S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi HAGL. 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n th\u1eafng 2 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 sau 90 ph\u00fat so t\u00e0i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7&nbsp;Vincent Bossou. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i binh, HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2, d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec trong tay \u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e1ng lo nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 V-League. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 22/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 15 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Lich-thi-dau-vong-15-V-League.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018: HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\">Thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HAGL s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi?</span><br />\r\nSau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3754","checkdouble":"189221"},{"date":"06:46 22/06","title":"\u0102n burger mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi n\u1ebfu ... c\u00f3 b\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/an-burger-mien-phi-tron-doi-neu-co-bau-voi-cau-thu-du-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m t\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00f3i tr\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u1eeba qua, chu\u1ed7i c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0103n nhanh Burger King tung chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean VK, m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Facebook c\u1ee7a Nga.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m m\u00f9a World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Quang-cao-Burger-King-tai-Nga-phan-cam-mua-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang b\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup \u1edf Nga c\u1ee7a Burger King tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng VK. \u1ea2nh: Deadspin Photograph.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Burger King kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1eb7ng th\u01b0\u1edfng 3 tri\u1ec7u rup (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n 1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng) v\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi \u0103n burger Whoppers (l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Burger King v\u1edbi nh\u00e2n g\u1ed3m th\u1ecbt b\u00f2 n\u01b0\u1edbng, x\u00e0 l\u00e1ch, c\u00e0 chua, h\u00e0nh t\u00e2y v\u00e0 d\u01b0a mu\u1ed1i) cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00e0o c\u00f3 b\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay sau khi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, Burger King \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. C\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i xo\u00e1 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng VK.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nan nhan trong vu hiep dam bi Burger King Nga loi dung hinh anh cho chien dich quang cao. Anh: RT.\" title=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong v\u1ee5 hi\u1ebfp d\u00e2m b\u1ecb Burger King Nga l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. \u1ea2nh: RT.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BK_russia_1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong v\u1ee5 hi\u1ebfp d\u00e2m b\u1ecb Burger King Nga l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. \u1ea2nh: RT.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng Burger King t\u1ea1i Nga s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c thu h\u00fat d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eef thi\u1ebfu ni\u00ean 16 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb hi\u1ebfp d\u00e2m trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u1ecd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Diana Shurygina d\u00f9ng c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 tay \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u00f4 b\u00e9 \u0111\u00e3 u\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat r\u01b0\u1ee3u vodka trong b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh minh ho\u1ea1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i mua 1 t\u1eb7ng 1.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Nga m\u00e0 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Burger King mang ti\u1ebfng x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m t\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb em g\u00e1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Burger King Singapore loi dung hinh anh phu nu dang ha mieng va chu Blow - co nghia la thoi va de bi hieu nham mang tinh goi duc trong khau hieu quang cao san pham moi. Anh: Adweek.\" title=\"Burger King Singapore l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111ang h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eef Blow - c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u1ed5i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea7m mang t\u00ednh g\u1ee3i d\u1ee5c trong kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: Adweek.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bk_blow_ad_1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Burger King Singapore l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111ang h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eef Blow - c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u1ed5i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea7m mang t\u00ednh g\u1ee3i d\u1ee5c trong kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: Adweek.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u0103m 2009, t\u1ea1i Singapore, c\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00e1nh burger d\u00e0i 7 inch (17 cm) v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh g\u1ee3i d\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111ang h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 c\u00e2u kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u \u201cN\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y ng\u1ea5t ng\u00e2y\u201d.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu n\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p trong \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3753","checkdouble":"189214"}]}